        <mxCell id="qY9Yzxmkbyx34cncm8wa-78" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fillColor=#dae8fc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=1;fontSize=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;Seat Locking Flow (Critical Path for Consistency)&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;1. POST /v1/bookings arrives at Booking Service&#xa;2. Booking Service calls Redis SETNX seat:{show_id}:{seat_id} = user_id (TTL=5min)&#xa;3. If SETNX returns 0 → seat already locked → reject immediately&#xa;4. If SETNX returns 1 → seat locked → proceed to Payment Service&#xa;5. Payment success → DB write (status=BOOKED) → Kafka event → Redis key deleted&#xa;6. Payment fail / TTL expires → lock auto-releases → seat returns to AVAILABLE" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="760" x="990" y="1355" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qY9Yzxmkbyx34cncm8wa-79" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="420" x="990" y="1500" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qY9Yzxmkbyx34cncm8wa-80" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="20" width="200" x="1005" y="1510" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
